  <h2>Permitting &amp; inspections with Pasco County Building Services</h2>
  <p>Any Pasco County HVAC replacement, duct modification, or electrical subpanel upgrade requires a mechanical permit. We handle the entire process: submittal, plan review, rough inspection if required, and final. We\u2019re on a first-name basis with Pasco County\u2019s mechanical inspectors — in practice that means faster turnaround and fewer re-inspections. You get an emailed PDF of the closed permit for your records and closing docs.</p>

